<plot>DAYS LIKE THESE is a comedy about an unlucky young man, Zach, and his efforts to make it to a first date with the sultry and impatient Nikki. As the forces of nature conspire against him, Zach finds himself on an unexpected adventure through the city where he meets a cast of characters connected by objects and events spanning five decades of time. His predicament forces him to make a decision: Will he accept or reject what the universe has planned for him?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?130758</url></doc>
